sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant CL as Client
  participant API as API
  CL->>API: GET /items?limit=100
  API-->>CL: 200 OK { items..., next_cursor }
  alt more pages
    CL-->>CL: Store next_cursor, process page
    CL->>API: GET /items?limit=100&cursor=next_cursor
    API-->>CL: 200 OK { items..., next_cursor }
  else done
    CL-->>CL: No next_cursor, complete
  end
  Note over CL,API: Backoff on 429/503 and resume with last cursor
